{
  "stem": "3380.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother decided that I should go back and discuss the situation, and tell the-- my father, and what should we do next.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we cannot be there forever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Russians, what-- at that time, they're insist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would like us that we should accept their citizenship-- Russian citizenship papers-- and ship us out to Soviet Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't-- they-- they meant well, because there was no work, I mean.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was hundreds of thousands of Jews escaping from the Germans right there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, that was no place where to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I was not successful crossing the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I came back to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Coming back to Bialystok, I have seen that my brother was not there anymore, and he forgot to leave the address.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He probably assumed that I crossed the border and it's good that it's going.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was looking for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was looking for about six or seven weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very lonely-- no place where to stay, no place-- I mean, except for the Tannenbaum family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I decided to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came back, I find my brother Efroim at home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took-- already organized another group of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he went back to Soviet Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remained in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Lask.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they made a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took the worst neighborhood in the city, and they put all the people, I mean, where to live in certain areas, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They allocated a part-- this is the-- this is the place where Jews are gonna live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rest of them had to go in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 19-- 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our street-- we used to live-- that was-- that-- that was part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
